WEBVTT

00:23.719 --> 00:26.330
We need Jose Battle
to keep the peace.

00:26.330 --> 00:28.680
We need Bumpy Johnson
to sell our dope in Harlem.

00:28.680 --> 00:30.378
Go fuck yourselves.

00:31.683 --> 00:33.555
Your friends ask you to
come and try to change my mind?

00:33.555 --> 00:37.037
I'd rather be friends
with an Alzado.

00:37.037 --> 00:40.083
I spoke with Assistant District
Attorney Pike today.

00:40.083 --> 00:42.259
He knows about your association
with Jose Battle.

00:42.259 --> 00:46.046
- Who do you want me to kill?
- Juan Madera, a journalist.

00:46.046 --> 00:49.092
I keep my promises.

00:49.092 --> 00:50.615
Better keep yours.

00:50.615 --> 00:53.053
I would love for you to come
with me to Africa.

00:53.053 --> 00:55.881
I'll need an executive assistant
to help with my affairs.

00:55.881 --> 00:59.059
- Travel to Africa with you?
- Who better than you?

00:59.059 --> 01:00.973
How long are you
keeping me here for?

01:00.973 --> 01:03.889
Someone tried
to have you killed.

01:03.889 --> 01:06.762
I made a promise to your pops
that I'd look after you.

01:06.762 --> 01:08.894
- This is an easy gig here.
- What if I quit?

01:08.894 --> 01:10.200
Then you stay in your room.

01:10.200 --> 01:11.375
We'll discuss salary
over dinner.

01:11.375 --> 01:12.724
Fine.

01:12.724 --> 01:15.162
There's no reason
why we can't be friends.

01:17.033 --> 01:19.122
I'll take him back
to French Connection.

01:19.122 --> 01:21.472
We found Monsieur 98.

01:21.472 --> 01:23.126
Who scares you the most?

01:23.126 --> 01:24.562
Bonnano or me?

01:26.477 --> 01:28.088
I will take your side.

01:28.088 --> 01:29.741
Three thousand keys.

01:29.741 --> 01:31.613
With the biggest
duji shipment in history.

01:37.314 --> 01:41.492
So, I received this postcard
from our man in Marseilles.

01:41.492 --> 01:43.842
His name is Jean Cesar,

01:43.842 --> 01:47.759
but he's better known
as Monsieur 98.

01:47.759 --> 01:49.631
Well, in case
you didn't know it,

01:49.631 --> 01:52.503
we've been dealing
with these fuckin' frogs

01:52.503 --> 01:54.505
before you had diapers on.

01:54.505 --> 01:56.507
What are you saying?

01:56.507 --> 01:58.640
I'm saying that
on the last shipment,

01:58.640 --> 02:00.859
Bumpy Johnson made you all
look like idiots.

02:00.859 --> 02:03.166
- Hey, hey, you fuckin'--
- Hey, Carlo, let him talk.

02:03.166 --> 02:04.515
What are you saying?

02:04.515 --> 02:06.256
If he hadn't had
the rotten luck

02:06.256 --> 02:08.040
for the dope
to burn up in those riots,

02:08.040 --> 02:10.782
he'd be in control
of the connection right now.

02:10.782 --> 02:13.437
As it is, Monsieur 98
is coming soon

02:13.437 --> 02:15.309
to work out an arrangement
with anyone

02:15.309 --> 02:18.007
that has the organization
and the police protection

02:18.007 --> 02:20.444
to move the junk
into the neighborhoods.

02:20.444 --> 02:23.012
Where does Chin stand
on all this?

02:23.012 --> 02:26.363
He's authorized me
to negotiate a deal,

02:26.363 --> 02:28.800
with your approval, of course,

02:28.800 --> 02:31.803
and to keep Bumpy Johnson away
from this deal at all costs.

02:31.803 --> 02:34.154
Good luck with that.

02:34.154 --> 02:35.633
See this?

02:35.633 --> 02:37.505
This nigger was just put in
as the captain

02:37.505 --> 02:39.507
of the 27th Precinct.

02:39.507 --> 02:42.727
Him and Johnson are gonna be
thick as thieves.

02:42.727 --> 02:46.731
Listen, this guy was installed
to calm the Blacks in Harlem

02:46.731 --> 02:49.865
after the riots
so they see a Black face.

02:49.865 --> 02:52.911
That's it. He's a figurehead.
Nothing more.

02:52.911 --> 02:57.655
No one could move dope in Harlem
<i>without</i> the 27th in pocket.

02:57.655 --> 03:01.398
Not you, not me,
not even Johnson.

03:03.705 --> 03:06.316
Calm down, fellas.

03:06.316 --> 03:09.450
Cops don't give a flying fuck
about Black or white.

03:10.929 --> 03:12.583
It's all about green.

03:43.397 --> 03:44.572
Listen.

03:46.269 --> 03:48.228
We're not gonna have
a problem, right?

03:48.228 --> 03:50.882
There's always problems
when you move the duji.

03:50.882 --> 03:53.058
No, I mean
with this new cop,

03:53.058 --> 03:55.452
this new captain guy--
he's not gonna fuck us up?

03:55.452 --> 03:59.369
It depends on whether he bleeds
Black or he bleeds blue.

03:59.369 --> 04:02.067
I'm more worried about Colombo
and the Families.

04:02.067 --> 04:04.983
They've always been able to work
things out with the cops.

04:08.248 --> 04:10.772
Everyone down on
the fucking floor right now!

04:12.382 --> 04:14.993
Everyone!

04:16.995 --> 04:18.432
- Get down, you motherfuckers.
- Get down!

04:18.432 --> 04:20.303
Everybody down
on the fucking ground!

04:20.303 --> 04:21.565
Get down on the fucking floor.
Are you stupid?

04:21.565 --> 04:23.567
- Get the fuck down.
- You can't hear me?

04:23.567 --> 04:26.744
Everybody down
on the floor now!

04:26.744 --> 04:30.052
Get the fuck down
on the floor now, everyone!

