05:02.867 --> 05:05.348
<i>♪ Just in case</i>

05:05.348 --> 05:07.829
<i>♪ Lay on my back
watchin' the ceilin' fan ♪</i>

05:07.829 --> 05:10.440
<i>♪ I had a dream to
touch a kilo gram ♪</i>

05:10.440 --> 05:12.616
<i>♪ Still at odds
with the Irish mob ♪</i>

05:12.616 --> 05:15.227
<i>♪ Rolls-Royce down
Malcolm X Boulevard ♪</i>

05:15.227 --> 05:18.492
<i>♪ Lord, these-- really
out here preyin' on me ♪</i>

05:18.492 --> 05:20.972
<i>♪ Got the .40 on me
and his hand on me ♪</i>

05:20.972 --> 05:23.235
<i>♪ Snow-white mink
like I'm Dutch Schultz ♪</i>

05:23.235 --> 05:26.369
<i>♪ Run the books and let me
show you how the numbers look ♪</i>

05:26.369 --> 05:28.980
<i>♪ You can't be lucky
like you Luciano ♪</i>

05:28.980 --> 05:31.722
<i>♪ The kilos slammin'
like they new pianos ♪</i>

05:31.722 --> 05:34.464
<i>♪ And Fat Boy got the big body</i>

05:34.464 --> 05:36.553
<i>♪ Coast-to-coast,
I could shoot product ♪</i>

