05:56.007 --> 05:58.270
<i>♪ I keep
a revolver with your name ♪</i>

05:58.270 --> 06:00.447
<i>♪ Just in case</i>

06:02.536 --> 06:04.755
They did this shit
in my fucking house?

06:04.755 --> 06:06.888
My fucking house?

06:07.976 --> 06:10.239
Do cops usually
come after you like this?

06:10.239 --> 06:12.067
No.

06:12.067 --> 06:14.765
I got cops on the pad
to protect this place.

06:14.765 --> 06:18.552
Maybe somebody's paying them
more money to stand aside.

06:18.552 --> 06:22.512
I didn't recognize those two,
but I saw their brass.

06:22.512 --> 06:24.514
They're from the 27th.

06:24.514 --> 06:26.734
Motherfuckers took money
outta the tip jar,

06:26.734 --> 06:28.736
but didn't even go back
and look for a safe.

06:28.736 --> 06:32.522
Fucking intimidation move.

06:32.522 --> 06:35.699
Colombo sending a message?

06:35.699 --> 06:39.790
Yeah, well, he sees that you
and me, we're raking it in.

06:39.790 --> 06:42.097
It's a fuck-you.

06:42.097 --> 06:45.230
How about we get some men
and we go hit <i>him</i> back?

06:45.230 --> 06:48.146
It's not about
tit for tat.

06:48.146 --> 06:50.235
This is about the heroin.

06:50.235 --> 06:52.412
Colombo's making his play.

06:52.412 --> 06:53.891
Shipment's coming in.

06:53.891 --> 06:57.591
If he gets the 27th,
we're fucked.

07:19.482 --> 07:21.179
Bon voyage.

07:25.009 --> 07:27.359
<i>The people of Harlem need
to trust their men in uniform,</i>

07:27.359 --> 07:29.666
<i>and we need
to earn their trust.</i>

07:29.666 --> 07:31.973
<i>For too long, policing in
Harlem has been</i>

07:31.973 --> 07:35.759
<i>billy club first,
questions later, if at all,</i>

07:35.759 --> 07:38.327
<i>and I can promise you
that will change.</i>

07:39.502 --> 07:43.288
Oh, thank God you're okay.

07:43.288 --> 07:44.899
They shot up the place.

07:46.640 --> 07:48.772
- Cops?
- In uniform.

07:48.772 --> 07:50.295
I'm telling you,
those cops were bought

07:50.295 --> 07:51.601
and paid for by the guineas.

07:54.691 --> 07:56.127
You know what, Elsworth?

07:56.127 --> 07:57.215
There might be a way
you can deal with this

07:57.215 --> 08:00.480
by going
right to the source.

08:00.480 --> 08:02.177
What do you mean?

08:02.177 --> 08:04.875
Well, Reggie Fields
was just on the news--

08:04.875 --> 08:06.181
the new police captain.

08:06.181 --> 08:07.530
I met him with Roy Wingate
last week.

08:07.530 --> 08:09.663
He is an honest, good man.

08:09.663 --> 08:11.012
And he's Black.

08:14.058 --> 08:15.712
What difference
does that make?

08:15.712 --> 08:17.148
Well, he says he wants to make
a difference in Harlem,

08:17.148 --> 08:18.628
and I believe him.

08:18.628 --> 08:20.543
If there are dirty, corrupt cops
on his force,

08:20.543 --> 08:22.153
he should know about it.

08:22.153 --> 08:24.025
I also have cops on the pad, Mayme.

08:26.375 --> 08:29.204
Look.

08:29.204 --> 08:33.034
They don't steal from
legitimate businesses.

08:33.034 --> 08:36.864
You are a Black business owner.
You have rights.

08:36.864 --> 08:39.867
You think this new captain
gives a shit about me?

08:39.867 --> 08:41.521
He should.

08:44.262 --> 08:46.177
You're always looking out
for me, aren't you?

08:46.177 --> 08:48.179
Just talk to him,

08:48.179 --> 08:50.530
make him aware
of the situation.

09:03.064 --> 09:05.327
It feels like we landed
in a postcard.

09:07.590 --> 09:08.852
If I remember
the guidebook,

09:08.852 --> 09:11.420
that's the Great Pyramid
of Giza.

09:11.420 --> 09:13.378
You're not homesick yet?

09:13.378 --> 09:15.903
Harlem has its glory, but...

09:15.903 --> 09:19.123
Ghana, Nigeria, Sudan--

09:19.123 --> 09:21.082
Africa's starting to feel
like my real home.

09:21.082 --> 09:25.260
Yeah, you're hearing
our ancestors' voices clearly

09:25.260 --> 09:28.263
for the first time,

09:28.263 --> 09:31.875
unfiltered by
the fog of prejudice.

09:31.875 --> 09:35.096
I bet it soothes your soul
as it does mine.

09:37.968 --> 09:41.232
You have tea with President
Gamal Abdel Nasser at 4:00

09:41.232 --> 09:44.148
and then dinner with President
Ahmed Ben Bella of Algeria,

09:44.148 --> 09:45.410
if you can manage.

09:45.410 --> 09:46.716
Call them both
and reschedule.

09:46.716 --> 09:48.065
Why?

09:48.065 --> 09:49.458
Che Guevara wants
to meet with me today.

09:49.458 --> 09:51.591
The Cuban revolutionary.

09:51.591 --> 09:54.419
He sent me a telegram
when we were both in Accra.

09:54.419 --> 09:57.640
He wants to meet before I speak
at the Pan-African Conference.

09:57.640 --> 10:00.121
I'll clear your schedule.

10:00.121 --> 10:01.644
Anything else?

10:01.644 --> 10:03.080
I'm gonna go to that bazaar
near the hotel.

10:03.080 --> 10:04.647
I want to get a gift
for Margaret.

10:04.647 --> 10:07.737
Look, I don't want you to leave
this hotel on your own.

10:07.737 --> 10:09.130
Why?

10:09.130 --> 10:12.437
All over Africa,
I've gone as I pleased.

10:12.437 --> 10:15.005
Egypt is a different beast.

10:15.005 --> 10:17.660
There are proprieties in place,
especially for women.

10:17.660 --> 10:21.272
It's far more stringent
than in West Africa.

10:21.272 --> 10:24.624
I think you should
stay in your room.

10:24.624 --> 10:27.670
I will, as soon as I finish
arranging your schedule.

10:41.858 --> 10:45.383
Here is your money.

10:45.383 --> 10:47.995
Thank you for a job well done.

10:50.562 --> 10:53.522
What exactly was the point
of all that bullshit?

10:53.522 --> 10:57.700
Call it the fine art
of negotiation.

10:57.700 --> 11:01.312
Now, how many cops
does Johnson still have

11:01.312 --> 11:02.966
in his pocket at the 27?

11:02.966 --> 11:06.404
Look at the bodacious tatas
on this girl.

11:06.404 --> 11:09.016
Jesus mother of Mary.

11:09.016 --> 11:10.844
Still gonna be a while
till we find out which cops

11:10.844 --> 11:12.584
Johnson controls.

11:12.584 --> 11:15.413
What about
this new captain?

11:15.413 --> 11:18.242
I need him on my pad
when the shipment comes in.

11:18.242 --> 11:21.811
With Chin Gigante gone,
you're making a play, huh?

11:21.811 --> 11:23.552
The fuck are
you talking about?

11:25.772 --> 11:27.382
What?

11:27.382 --> 11:30.211
I'm holding down the fort
<i>for</i> Chin Gigante.

11:30.211 --> 11:34.737
They key is neutralizing
Bumpy Johnson.

11:34.737 --> 11:36.739
How the fuck
we supposed to do that?

11:36.739 --> 11:37.827
Arrest him.

11:37.827 --> 11:39.350
On what charge?

11:39.350 --> 11:41.570
I don't fucking know.
Who cares?

11:41.570 --> 11:44.573
I just need to show him
who's boss around here.

11:44.573 --> 11:47.402
Maybe a couple days at Rikers
will change his attitude.

11:50.666 --> 11:52.276
Yeah.

11:54.975 --> 11:57.194
Thanks for seeing me,
Captain Fields.

11:57.194 --> 11:59.893
My wife-- she speaks
very highly of you.

12:01.895 --> 12:03.723
According to this report,
Mr. Johnson,

12:03.723 --> 12:07.030
your Geechee club is open past
the hours of legal operation.

12:07.030 --> 12:09.598
Most of the clubs in Harlem
do that, Captain,

12:09.598 --> 12:11.774
as you must well know.

12:11.774 --> 12:14.951
My place was shot up
by your police officers

12:14.951 --> 12:16.866
for no reason whatsoever.

12:16.866 --> 12:18.781
Well, that's quite
an accusation.

12:18.781 --> 12:20.609
I mean,
I didn't recognize them,

12:20.609 --> 12:24.918
but they were wearing uniforms
and 27th Precinct badges.

12:24.918 --> 12:28.095
My question is,
what are you doing about it?

12:28.095 --> 12:29.749
If what you say is true,

12:29.749 --> 12:32.403
an independent counsel
would have to be convened,

12:32.403 --> 12:34.666
which would take considerable
amounts of time and money.

12:34.666 --> 12:36.103
That's an excellent idea.

12:36.103 --> 12:37.757
Resources which could
be used instead

12:37.757 --> 12:40.498
to investigate racketeering, prostitution,

12:40.498 --> 12:42.979
loan sharking, numbers running,
and dope peddling.

12:42.979 --> 12:45.808
But not police corruption,
I guess.

12:45.808 --> 12:49.769
Johnson, let's get
past the bullshit.

12:49.769 --> 12:51.118
Mm.

12:51.118 --> 12:52.989
I know who you are
and your long rap sheet.

12:52.989 --> 12:55.600
I also know the many things
you do to help the community,

12:55.600 --> 12:57.907
like all those kids
you help send to college.

12:57.907 --> 13:00.344
I do what I can.
What about you?

13:00.344 --> 13:02.912
Well, there are many things
I need to concern myself with,

13:02.912 --> 13:05.654
and dirty cops
<i>is</i> one of them.

13:05.654 --> 13:07.787
But so are mob bosses,

13:07.787 --> 13:09.658
both Italian and Black.

13:11.660 --> 13:14.706
Your complaint is
duly noted.

13:14.706 --> 13:16.708
I guess that means
that you're not gonna do

13:16.708 --> 13:19.276
a goddamn thing about it, then.

13:19.276 --> 13:24.804
Know this-- if you can't keep
your cops under control,

13:24.804 --> 13:27.850
you can bet your Black ass
that I will.

13:44.867 --> 13:46.477
Nice of you to show up.

13:46.477 --> 13:49.045
Oh, I didn't know you kept
strict business hours.

13:49.045 --> 13:50.525
Yeah, I don't,

13:50.525 --> 13:52.832
but a little discipline
wouldn't hurt.

13:52.832 --> 13:54.311
Well, that's not gonna
help me much,

13:54.311 --> 13:57.227
seeing I don't do nothing
but take messages for you.

13:59.534 --> 14:01.841
That's right.
You take messages for me.

14:01.841 --> 14:03.364
And I'm keeping you alive.

14:03.364 --> 14:05.540
Seems like
a fair trade to me.

14:05.540 --> 14:07.585
Keeping me alive for what?

14:07.585 --> 14:09.500
I'm bored. I'm lonely.

14:09.500 --> 14:11.676
I can't go anywhere
or do anything.

14:11.676 --> 14:13.287
I have no friends.

14:19.946 --> 14:23.688
What can I do to put a smile
on that pretty face of yours?

14:23.688 --> 14:25.908
You can give me
my freedom.

14:25.908 --> 14:27.170
Let me go to Paris.

14:29.738 --> 14:32.872
I get that you're bored
and lonely.

14:34.917 --> 14:37.006
How about that Negro lady
you saw in Philly?

14:37.006 --> 14:38.921
You want I should bring her
up here for a visit?

14:38.921 --> 14:40.705
The last thing I want
is your fucking goons

14:40.705 --> 14:42.185
running in on her
with their guns

14:42.185 --> 14:44.753
and forcing her
to do anything.

14:44.753 --> 14:45.928
Okay.

14:45.928 --> 14:49.105
You're such
a fucking asshole!

14:49.105 --> 14:50.715
Forget I mentioned it.

14:50.715 --> 14:53.370
Forget I offered
to do anything!

14:53.370 --> 14:54.937
You're such an ungrateful
little bitch.

14:54.937 --> 14:56.808
If I didn't make a promise
to your father

14:56.808 --> 14:58.027
that I'd keep you safe,

14:58.027 --> 15:00.073
I'd consider
whacking you myself!

15:03.076 --> 15:05.295
Fuck you!

15:08.646 --> 15:11.649
Malcolm X in the flesh.

15:11.649 --> 15:14.739
Che Guevara.

15:14.739 --> 15:17.133
What an honor
to finally meet you.

15:17.133 --> 15:21.268
Fidel, uh, often spoke
about his wonderful trip

15:21.268 --> 15:24.401
to Harlem and your gifts
as an orator.

15:24.401 --> 15:26.403
He described you

15:26.403 --> 15:29.754
as "America's
number-one revolutionary."

15:29.754 --> 15:32.061
I'm pleased by Fidel's
kind words.

15:32.061 --> 15:35.978
They are his words,
not mine.

15:35.978 --> 15:39.764
I would not call you
a revolutionary.

15:39.764 --> 15:41.679
How would you
describe me, then?

15:41.679 --> 15:43.551
If you don't mind
my asking.

15:47.337 --> 15:49.774
As an advocate, perhaps,

15:49.774 --> 15:52.995
but a revolutionary fights
with more than just his words.

15:52.995 --> 15:55.258
He takes action.

15:55.258 --> 15:57.957
I have never backed down
from a fight.

15:57.957 --> 16:00.350
You are Minister Malcolm X.

16:00.350 --> 16:01.961
If you sound a war cry,

16:01.961 --> 16:04.485
all of heaven and Earth
will take arms.

16:07.227 --> 16:08.532
This is about the speech
I'm making

16:08.532 --> 16:10.491
at the Pan-African Conference.

16:10.491 --> 16:12.449
You can be of great service.

16:12.449 --> 16:14.886
I need the African leaders
to lend their support

16:14.886 --> 16:17.977
to the worldwide struggle
for liberation.

16:17.977 --> 16:21.328
They eat out of your hands.

16:21.328 --> 16:22.851
They listen to you.

16:22.851 --> 16:26.333
I am here to talk about
<i>our</i> people's

16:26.333 --> 16:30.032
political struggle
in the United States.

16:30.032 --> 16:32.469
You're always talking
about the crimes committed

16:32.469 --> 16:33.862
against your people

16:33.862 --> 16:36.212
by racist forces
in <i>your</i> country.

16:36.212 --> 16:37.735
They are too great
to mention.

16:37.735 --> 16:40.129
If you can't see that
your country is committing

16:40.129 --> 16:42.523
these crimes
all over the world,

16:42.523 --> 16:44.351
then why are you here?

16:47.528 --> 16:50.139
Or is it just to see
the pyramids?

17:02.586 --> 17:03.935
Who is it?

17:03.935 --> 17:05.589
Hotel security.

17:09.811 --> 17:11.856
How can I help you?

17:11.856 --> 17:14.033
Is Malcolm El Shabazz present?

17:14.033 --> 17:15.904
No, I'm sorry.
He's at a meeting.

17:15.904 --> 17:18.037
Are you the assistant
to Malcolm El Shabazz?

17:18.037 --> 17:19.603
Yes.

17:19.603 --> 17:20.735
Please come with me.

17:20.735 --> 17:22.084
Why?

17:22.084 --> 17:23.868
Please follow me.

17:32.790 --> 17:34.401
Thank you.

17:37.839 --> 17:39.406
I'm sure you're wondering
why hotel security

17:39.406 --> 17:40.755
asked you down here.

17:40.755 --> 17:42.191
No one asked me.

17:42.191 --> 17:43.932
If they had,
I wouldn't have come.

17:46.152 --> 17:48.545
Fair enough.

17:48.545 --> 17:50.199
My name is
Gregory Reynolds.

17:50.199 --> 17:51.766
I'm with the U.S.
State Department.

17:51.766 --> 17:53.463
I wanted to have
a little talk with you

17:53.463 --> 17:56.292
about Malcolm El Shabazz.

17:56.292 --> 17:57.902
What about him?

17:57.902 --> 17:59.121
Well, we understand
that you've been traveling

17:59.121 --> 18:01.906
as his secretary
throughout Africa,

18:01.906 --> 18:03.647
and that he trusts you.

18:03.647 --> 18:05.736
Why not talk to him
yourself?

18:05.736 --> 18:09.218
We both know he's a very
proud man and stubborn,

18:09.218 --> 18:11.177
and doesn't always
listen to reason.

18:14.528 --> 18:15.572
We don't want him
to give a speech

18:15.572 --> 18:17.748
at the Pan-African Conference.

18:17.748 --> 18:19.141
Why?

18:19.141 --> 18:20.925
We know that Malcolm
and Che Guevara

18:20.925 --> 18:22.753
have been in communication.

18:22.753 --> 18:24.625
Spreading communist propaganda
in Africa

18:24.625 --> 18:27.454
is against
our national interest.

18:27.454 --> 18:29.369
Who exactly are you?

18:31.458 --> 18:35.026
Africa's a tinder box
right now.

18:35.026 --> 18:37.246
Wars breaking out all over.

18:37.246 --> 18:38.769
The Communists would like
nothing more

18:38.769 --> 18:41.032
than to form
a stronghold here.

18:41.032 --> 18:43.774
What in the world does that
have to do with Malcolm?

18:43.774 --> 18:46.603
When he talks
about things like...

18:46.603 --> 18:50.129
liberation and resistance,

18:50.129 --> 18:54.872
it's just a <i>very</i> short hop
to socialism and communism.

18:54.872 --> 18:56.526
Malcolm is no communist.

18:58.049 --> 19:01.444
Look, he's free to say
whatever he wants

19:01.444 --> 19:03.881
on American soil.

19:03.881 --> 19:05.796
But in Egypt,
the State Department would

19:05.796 --> 19:07.798
prefer he cancel
his speech.

19:07.798 --> 19:09.496
No way
he's gonna cancel.

19:14.196 --> 19:17.547
Rumor has it that someone
from Mosque Number Seven

19:17.547 --> 19:20.028
in New York City
tried to kill him.

19:20.028 --> 19:21.682
Is that correct?

19:23.945 --> 19:26.382
I have no idea.

19:26.382 --> 19:29.994
Miss Johnson,

19:29.994 --> 19:31.822
I know you care
about this man,

19:31.822 --> 19:33.868
and, believe it or not,
so do I.

19:33.868 --> 19:37.480
I want to see
that he makes it home safe.

19:37.480 --> 19:40.048
He certainly doesn't need
more enemies.

19:43.269 --> 19:46.054
Only one?

19:46.054 --> 19:48.012
What?

19:48.012 --> 19:51.233
We had two dozen patrol and
three detectives on our books.

19:51.233 --> 19:54.236
I want to know
what the fuck happened.

19:54.236 --> 19:56.673
We-- We did the footwork
like you asked.

19:56.673 --> 19:58.414
And these cops
we've known for years

19:58.414 --> 20:00.416
barely even <i>willing</i>
to talk to us.

20:00.416 --> 20:03.376
Whoever got to our cops either
put the fear of God in 'em

20:03.376 --> 20:05.116
or is paying them
a whole lot more.

20:05.116 --> 20:07.858
Either way, Colombo.

20:07.858 --> 20:09.338
Any luck with
that new captain?

20:09.338 --> 20:10.687
Useless.

20:10.687 --> 20:12.211
Another token Negro
to con our people

20:12.211 --> 20:13.864
into thinking
that things are changing.

20:13.864 --> 20:16.258
Now what about those fuckers
who hit the Geechee?

20:16.258 --> 20:18.086
Still making inquiries.

20:20.436 --> 20:22.090
Without cops on our pad,

20:22.090 --> 20:25.615
we're looking at a life sentence
if we get pinched.

20:25.615 --> 20:27.443
What do you suggest?

20:31.317 --> 20:32.970
What about D'Alessandro?

20:32.970 --> 20:36.278
Nah, nah, he ain't in the 27th.
He's Midtown.

20:36.278 --> 20:37.801
I don't care.

20:37.801 --> 20:39.760
If you want information
about dirty cops,

20:39.760 --> 20:42.110
you ask a dirty cop.

20:42.110 --> 20:43.677
Get me D'Alessandro.

20:47.289 --> 20:49.900
So let me
get this straight.

20:49.900 --> 20:53.295
Joseph Colombo
is keeping you prisoner?

20:53.295 --> 20:55.906
At my father's request.

20:55.906 --> 20:59.432
He's worried one of the other
Families might try to kill me.

20:59.432 --> 21:01.651
So how exactly are you
a prisoner?

21:01.651 --> 21:04.263
He got me an apartment
where I gotta stay.

21:04.263 --> 21:07.266
I work for him in his office
at the car lot.

21:07.266 --> 21:09.311
He has guards on me
all the time.

21:09.311 --> 21:10.791
The only reason
I'm here right now

21:10.791 --> 21:15.665
is 'cause I told them
I had a gynecological exam.

21:15.665 --> 21:19.278
So you're in close proximity
to Joe Colombo.

21:19.278 --> 21:21.018
Unfortunately, yes.

21:26.502 --> 21:28.809
Want Joe Colombo
out of your hair for good?

21:31.725 --> 21:34.118
We've been picking up chatter
about a huge shipment of heroin

21:34.118 --> 21:36.425
coming into New York.

21:36.425 --> 21:38.645
Connect him
to that shipment,

21:38.645 --> 21:40.777
and we'll put him away
for life.

21:40.777 --> 21:42.953
How the hell am I supposed
to do that?

21:42.953 --> 21:44.999
Get a couple glasses of wine
in these guys,

21:44.999 --> 21:47.175
they'll tell you
the riddle of the Sphinx.

21:47.175 --> 21:48.785
So you want me
to do your job for you

21:48.785 --> 21:51.048
and maybe
get myself killed?

21:51.048 --> 21:52.702
No, thanks.

21:52.702 --> 21:54.704
I'll make sure you get
a new identity, new life,

21:54.704 --> 21:56.402
under federal protection.

21:59.056 --> 22:01.189
Can you do that for me
in Paris?

22:05.062 --> 22:07.369
Normally we don't protect
people internationally.

22:09.676 --> 22:12.983
But you put Colombo in jail,

22:12.983 --> 22:15.029
you'll be walking
on the Champs-Elysées.

22:20.426 --> 22:22.210
What would I have to do?

22:23.298 --> 22:24.908
Bumpy, I'm sorry.

22:24.908 --> 22:28.390
I'm Midtown these days,
not anywhere near the 27th.

22:28.390 --> 22:32.002
I'm looking for the two
dirty cops who shot up my joint.

22:32.002 --> 22:33.482
How much would it cost me
to find out?

22:33.482 --> 22:35.658
It ain't about money.

22:35.658 --> 22:37.356
I won't be able to get a peep
out of no one.

22:37.356 --> 22:38.879
That new boss, Colombo--

22:38.879 --> 22:40.707
he's got everyone
on his payroll.

22:40.707 --> 22:43.666
Apparently, the next
shipment's gonna be huge.

22:43.666 --> 22:46.016
I need you to try.

22:46.016 --> 22:49.368
If they think I'm sniffing
around for <i>you,</i>

22:49.368 --> 22:52.675
I'll get my balls
chopped off, honest.

22:52.675 --> 22:54.198
Remind me how much money
you made

22:54.198 --> 22:56.157
when I stole that duji
out of that police locker?

22:57.767 --> 23:01.075
I bet it put your kids
through college.

23:01.075 --> 23:03.730
There's more of that
if you can help me out.

23:07.647 --> 23:09.083
I'll do my best.

23:09.083 --> 23:10.737
I appreciate it.

23:23.445 --> 23:25.665
That crooked cop ain't gonna
do shit, right?

23:29.582 --> 23:31.453
What you thinkin', boss?

23:31.453 --> 23:34.413
We got the signal from
Marseilles dope's coming soon.

23:38.939 --> 23:41.942
I'm thinking...

23:41.942 --> 23:43.944
we gotta set a meeting
with Colombo.

23:46.468 --> 23:48.078
Him and me.

23:56.609 --> 23:58.654
He knew about
your meeting with Che.

23:58.654 --> 24:00.482
I didn't know what to say.

24:00.482 --> 24:02.963
State Department, my ass.

24:05.835 --> 24:08.838
That man was pure CIA.

24:08.838 --> 24:12.581
The U.S. government trying to
intimidate me, even overseas.

24:12.581 --> 24:13.930
That's not good.

24:13.930 --> 24:15.758
It is.

24:15.758 --> 24:18.805
It means I'm getting
under their skin.

24:18.805 --> 24:21.329
I know how important
this speech is

24:21.329 --> 24:22.983
and how much you've
accomplished already.

24:22.983 --> 24:24.637
All over the continent,
you've talked about the need

24:24.637 --> 24:25.942
for Black liberation.

24:25.942 --> 24:27.378
And I have to continue.

24:27.378 --> 24:28.945
This speech is
the pinnacle.

24:28.945 --> 24:32.079
I know.
I'm just a little concerned.

24:35.386 --> 24:39.521
I'm not going to let anyone
keep me from my work.

24:39.521 --> 24:40.957
Nor should you,

24:40.957 --> 24:43.786
but that man scared me.

24:43.786 --> 24:45.527
This isn't a game.

24:45.527 --> 24:48.965
Nobody knows that
more than me.

24:48.965 --> 24:52.882
Malcolm,
I have a bad feeling.

25:21.650 --> 25:25.262
Well, here we are again.

25:25.262 --> 25:28.831
Putting those cops on my club
was a big mistake.

25:28.831 --> 25:31.051
What makes you think
those were <i>my</i> cops?

25:31.051 --> 25:34.228
Stop with the bullshit.
I know you got the 27th.

25:34.228 --> 25:35.446
That ain't gonna stop me
from getting the heroin

25:35.446 --> 25:37.753
from Marseilles
when it drops.

25:37.753 --> 25:41.757
You're in no position
to make threats, Johnson.

25:41.757 --> 25:44.586
But I'm a reasonable man.

25:44.586 --> 25:46.196
I'm willing to negotiate.

25:46.196 --> 25:48.024
You never give up,
do you?

25:48.024 --> 25:49.591
I get what I want.

25:49.591 --> 25:50.766
And what is that?

25:50.766 --> 25:52.768
When the shipment comes in,

25:52.768 --> 25:55.205
there'll be a fight
for who controls it.

25:55.205 --> 25:56.424
- Yeah.
- No!

25:56.424 --> 25:58.469
I'm gonna get the dope,
all of it.

25:58.469 --> 26:00.559
But I am gonna need
your help selling it.

26:00.559 --> 26:01.690
It's that simple.

26:01.690 --> 26:03.213
I don't work
for you, Joe.

26:04.737 --> 26:06.956
You know, Bumpy,

26:06.956 --> 26:09.306
you're always talking about

26:09.306 --> 26:10.786
how the Blacks
are mistreated.

26:10.786 --> 26:13.049
Listen, I don't disagree,

26:13.049 --> 26:16.444
so I made you a good offer
by any measure,

26:16.444 --> 26:18.098
a-and you turn me down.

26:18.098 --> 26:19.621
Again and again.

26:19.621 --> 26:22.058
Then you talk about
being locked in a cage?

26:22.058 --> 26:24.147
That's your own bullshit.

26:24.147 --> 26:27.716
To be honest, I got half a mind
to think <i>you're</i> a racist.

26:27.716 --> 26:30.153
You want to make a deal
right now?

26:30.153 --> 26:32.634
Equal partners.

26:32.634 --> 26:34.070
50-50.

26:34.070 --> 26:35.768
50-50 you want?

26:35.768 --> 26:38.988
It's too late for you
to dictate terms.

26:38.988 --> 26:43.602
I stood up for a fair deal
on your behalf to the Families.

26:43.602 --> 26:46.343
You made me look foolish
in their eyes.

26:48.389 --> 26:50.913
Especially when you conned
Jose Battle to your side.

26:50.913 --> 26:55.178
And so
with all due respect,

26:55.178 --> 26:58.834
you can go fuck yourself.

26:58.834 --> 27:00.488
That's what I thought.

27:02.577 --> 27:05.624
Listen, those cops are gonna
be cracking down

27:05.624 --> 27:08.627
on every fuckin' place
you and Battle own.

27:08.627 --> 27:10.498
You can't control
all of the cops.

27:10.498 --> 27:13.109
Well...

27:13.109 --> 27:15.677
...I control
more than you.

27:15.677 --> 27:18.158
Come here.
I want to show you something.

27:30.692 --> 27:33.303
He was asking a lot of
questions, from what I'm told.

27:51.713 --> 27:54.324
You're willing to let
a little CIA hide-and-seek

27:54.324 --> 27:56.849
scare you
out of your mission?

27:56.849 --> 27:58.633
They targeted
my assistant.

28:00.591 --> 28:04.378
If anything happened to Elise,
I'd never forgive myself.

28:05.074 --> 28:09.383
Safety is a luxury
revolutionaries cannot afford.

28:09.383 --> 28:13.517
You have to decide
what is more important--

28:13.517 --> 28:16.912
your cause or your life.

28:16.912 --> 28:21.047
I am willing to die
for what I believe in,

28:21.047 --> 28:23.440
as long as others aren't
put in danger beside me.

28:23.440 --> 28:28.010
You are sounding a war cry
for your people the world over.

28:28.010 --> 28:30.447
You could fire a bullet
that ricochets

28:30.447 --> 28:32.754
all the way back
to Washington.

28:35.104 --> 28:37.193
Or you can run and hide.

28:47.029 --> 28:51.381
You really think the CIA will
kill you for giving that speech?

28:51.381 --> 28:52.774
They've done far worse.

28:52.774 --> 28:55.559
You've been roaming
this continent for weeks,

28:55.559 --> 28:59.041
doing and saying
as you please.

28:59.041 --> 29:03.045
If they wanted you dead, <i>camarada,</i>

29:03.045 --> 29:04.786
they would've
killed you already.

29:18.452 --> 29:22.064
I see you're actually doing
something around here.

29:22.064 --> 29:23.500
Your paperwork is
such a mess,

29:23.500 --> 29:27.113
I decided to try
and organize things a bit.

29:27.113 --> 29:28.984
Oh.

29:28.984 --> 29:31.639
Uh, thank you.
I appreciate you doing that.

29:31.639 --> 29:33.989
Figured I may as well
be useful around here.

29:33.989 --> 29:36.818
Well, don't let me interrupt.

29:36.818 --> 29:39.778
Joe.

29:39.778 --> 29:42.171
I want to apologize
for my behavior

29:42.171 --> 29:44.608
the last time we spoke.

29:44.608 --> 29:46.610
I got a lot of stress,
you know?

29:46.610 --> 29:50.092
And I want you to know
that I'm grateful to you,

29:50.092 --> 29:51.964
and I know I haven't
made it easy.

29:56.490 --> 29:58.753
What's easy in this life, right?

30:00.233 --> 30:01.800
So, no hard feelings?

30:04.193 --> 30:05.804
No.

30:08.371 --> 30:11.200
No hard feelings.

30:11.200 --> 30:13.463
And I'm sorry that...

30:13.463 --> 30:15.988
I lost my cool.

30:15.988 --> 30:18.468
It's okay.

30:18.468 --> 30:21.863
Look, you took me out
for dinner,

30:21.863 --> 30:24.997
and I want to
return the favor.

30:24.997 --> 30:27.651
If you want to
come by later tonight,

30:27.651 --> 30:29.958
I could make my famous
eggplant caponata.

30:29.958 --> 30:31.220
It's famous, huh?

30:31.220 --> 30:33.179
It's my dad's favorite.

30:33.179 --> 30:35.529
Yeah, uh...

30:35.529 --> 30:37.531
Sure. Okay.

30:38.924 --> 30:41.883
Say 8:00?

30:41.883 --> 30:43.363
Sounds good.

30:48.368 --> 30:50.109
Well, I appreciate
the recommendation.

30:52.198 --> 30:53.895
More coffee, Bumpy?

30:53.895 --> 30:55.549
No thanks, kiddo.

30:55.549 --> 30:57.725
Trying to cut back?

30:57.725 --> 30:59.596
Not sure
I wanna wake up.

31:02.164 --> 31:08.475
<i>♪ I was afraid that this day
would come♪</i>

31:11.043 --> 31:14.176
Hear you been
looking for us.

31:14.176 --> 31:15.917
You're the cops
who shot up my joint.

31:15.917 --> 31:17.266
Can I get you gentlemen
anything?

31:17.266 --> 31:19.007
We won't be long.

31:19.007 --> 31:22.271
We have a warrant
for your arrest.

31:22.271 --> 31:24.534
On what charge?

31:24.534 --> 31:25.884
What do you think?

31:25.884 --> 31:28.060
Racketeering, pimping,
loan sharking,

31:28.060 --> 31:29.713
so much to choose from.

31:29.713 --> 31:32.760
Put your fucking hands
behind your back.

31:32.760 --> 31:34.893
How much is Colombo
paying you?

31:34.893 --> 31:36.285
I'll double it.

31:36.285 --> 31:38.287
Are you resisting arrest?

31:38.287 --> 31:41.029
You know, it's funny what
happens when you resist arrest.

31:41.029 --> 31:42.944
Put your fucking hands
behind your back.

31:42.944 --> 31:44.815
Make me!

31:44.815 --> 31:46.730
What is going on here?

31:46.730 --> 31:49.037
These are the men
who shot up my club.

31:49.037 --> 31:51.518
They're arresting me
on Joe Colombo's orders.

31:52.998 --> 31:54.216
What is this?

31:54.216 --> 31:55.217
What did he do?

31:55.217 --> 31:56.436
He's a known criminal.

31:56.436 --> 31:57.654
What are you
arresting him for?

31:57.654 --> 31:58.917
He did nothing.

31:58.917 --> 32:00.614
- He's innocent!
- He's innocent.

32:02.833 --> 32:04.096
Leave him alone!

32:04.096 --> 32:05.140
Settle down.

32:05.140 --> 32:07.926
Look, settle down, please!

32:07.926 --> 32:10.102
I followed you here because
I know what you're up to.

32:10.102 --> 32:11.930
- But--
- Get out of here, Delano.

32:11.930 --> 32:14.802
That's an order.

32:14.802 --> 32:15.803
Both of you.

32:19.111 --> 32:21.287
Get out.

32:21.287 --> 32:24.246
I want to see you and O'Mally
in my office in an hour.

32:24.246 --> 32:29.425
<i>♪ All alone♪</i>

32:29.425 --> 32:31.340
You might have just
saved my life.

32:31.340 --> 32:33.864
I'm not the enemy,
Mr. Johnson.

32:33.864 --> 32:37.346
I'm trying my best to fix
a system that is flawed.

32:39.479 --> 32:42.047
Well, in any case, thanks.

32:43.831 --> 32:45.006
Pair of sevens.

32:45.006 --> 32:46.138
And all I got is nothing.

32:46.138 --> 32:47.139
- And what you got?
- Full house!

32:47.139 --> 32:48.705
- Again?
- Come on!

32:48.705 --> 32:50.272
Get the fuck up.
Junie, Junie!

32:50.272 --> 32:51.839
Get back
to your business.

32:51.839 --> 32:53.449
I need you two to go find
these cops for me now.

32:53.449 --> 32:55.321
But we don't even know
their names or what precinct--

32:55.321 --> 32:56.844
O'Mally and Delano.

32:56.844 --> 32:58.280
Remember their names.

32:58.280 --> 32:59.847
Burn 'em into your skulls.

32:59.847 --> 33:01.370
They paid me
a little visit.

33:01.370 --> 33:03.285
And what do you want us
to do when we find them?

33:03.285 --> 33:06.723
I want you to bring them
to Casa Havana, alive.

33:06.723 --> 33:10.118
Battle's got a little basement
there where we can <i>talk.</i>

33:10.118 --> 33:12.860
You want us
to kidnap two cops?

33:12.860 --> 33:14.644
That'll bring the Feds
on our ass.

33:14.644 --> 33:17.473
These guys need to learn
a little bit more about the law.

33:21.912 --> 33:23.479
You sure, Bump?

33:23.479 --> 33:26.395
Don't worry.
I'm not gonna kill anybody.

