anything about it.

40:37.086 --> 40:39.741
Now, if you ask me,
Joe Colombo's clean.

40:50.360 --> 40:52.319
What the fuck is this?

40:52.319 --> 40:53.494
I don't know.

40:53.494 --> 40:55.844
I mean, I did everything
you said.

40:55.844 --> 40:58.717
Is it my fault your stupid
machinery doesn't do the job?

41:21.479 --> 41:22.871
Hey.

41:22.871 --> 41:24.786
