41:58.254 --> 41:59.995
<i>to represent the interests</i>

41:59.995 --> 42:03.912
<i>of 22 million
African Americans</i>

42:03.912 --> 42:07.176
<i>whose rights
are being violated daily</i>

42:07.176 --> 42:10.919
<i>by the racism
of American imperialists.</i>

42:10.919 --> 42:16.098
We in America are your
long-lost brothers and sisters.

42:16.098 --> 42:19.449
<i>We were taken forcibly
in chains</i>

42:19.449 --> 42:21.277
<i>from this mother continent</i>

42:21.277 --> 42:26.282
<i>and now have spent
